CREATE TABLE
CREATE TABLE
CREATE TABLE
                     Table "public.students"
 Column |         Type          | Collation | Nullable | Default 
--------+-----------------------+-----------+----------+---------
 sid    | character(4)          |           | not null | 
 name   | character varying(50) |           | not null | 
 major  | character varying(30) |           |          | 
 year   | integer               |           | not null | 
 gpa    | numeric(3,2)          |           |          | 
Indexes:
    "students_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (sid)
Referenced by:
    TABLE "enrollments" CONSTRAINT "enrollments_sid_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (sid) REFERENCES students(sid)

                      Table "public.courses"
 Column  |          Type          | Collation | Nullable | Default 
---------+------------------------+-----------+----------+---------
 cid     | character(4)           |           | not null | 
 title   | character varying(100) |           | not null | 
 credits | numeric(2,1)           |           |          | 
Indexes:
    "courses_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (cid)
Check constraints:
    "courses_credits_check" CHECK (credits >= 0::numeric AND credits <= 1.5)
Referenced by:
    TABLE "enrollments" CONSTRAINT "enrollments_cid_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (cid) REFERENCES courses(cid)

               Table "public.enrollments"
 Column |     Type     | Collation | Nullable | Default 
--------+--------------+-----------+----------+---------
 sid    | character(4) |           | not null | 
 cid    | character(4) |           | not null | 
 grade  | character(2) |           |          | 
Indexes:
    "enrollments_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (sid, cid)
Check constraints:
    "enrollments_grade_check" CHECK ((grade = ANY (ARRAY['A+'::bpchar, 'A'::bpchar, 'B'::bpchar, 'C'::bpchar, 'D'::bpchar, 'F'::bpchar])) OR grade IS NULL)
Foreign-key constraints:
    "enrollments_cid_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (cid) REFERENCES courses(cid)
    "enrollments_sid_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (sid) REFERENCES students(sid)
